<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Formats in Zend_Locale xml data files do not respect typographic rules.
e. g. in cs (cs_CZ) locale, behind every period there should be a space:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 

insted of current 

</code></pre>

<p>the same way for date/time: Medium date format should be {{d. M. yyyy}} with spaces, Medium time format should be {{H.mm:ss}} - with a period between hour and minutes.</p>

<p>For other languages, someone else has to state typo rules, those described are valid for {{cs}} and, hopefully, for {{sk}}</p>

